Many players would like to play Among Us  Minecraft map, which is why I decided to create an Animation based on Among Us/Minecraft and show how the New Among Us Minecraft map might look like. I recreate an unusual tasks that could be performed in  Among Us Minecraft Secret Map. Let the survival begin. 

Inspiring by Among us Zombie, Pixel kingdom, Hornstromp Games, Among us Logic.

Don't forget to subscribe with the bell, so you don't miss my new videos.

localize.title: 在我们中间-秘密的我的世界地图
localize.description:
许多玩家喜欢在我们中间玩“我的世界”地图，这就是为什么我决定创建一个基于“在我们中/我的世界”的动画，并展示“在我们中新的”“我的世界”地图可能是什么样子。我重新创造了一个不同寻常的任务，可以在“我们之间的游戏”、“我的世界”和“秘密地图”中执行。“让生存开始吧。”

灵感来自我们当中的僵尸，像素王国，Hornstromp游戏，我们之间的逻辑。

别忘了用铃声订阅，这样你就不会错过我的新视频了。

在我们中间

previous.excerpt:
Duck Life is a game that I never thought I'd speedrun, but I definitely don't regret it. This game is in a class of its own.

Watch live at: http://twitch.tv/EazySpeezy

▶ Twitter: https://twitter.com/EazySpeezy
▶ Discord: https://discord.gg/Fz6Dtdq

Watch the world record run here: https://youtu.be/jkwzJMapPeU

My channel generally focuses on a more casual side of speedruns. With these videos I want to show off cool speedruns, explain how they work, and entertain. Hopefully you enjoy the content and maybe even take up speedrunning yourself, because it is truly a lot of fun!

#EazySpeezy #DuckLife #Speedrun

localize.title: 我决定飞奔“鸭子生活”，愉快地消灭了所有其他的鸭子。
localize.description:
“鸭子生活”是一款我从未想过会飞奔的游戏，但我绝对不后悔。这个游戏是独一无二的。

观看现场直播：http://twitch.tv/EazySpeezy

https://twitter.com/EazySpeezy：▶推特
不和谐：https://discord.gg/Fz6Dtdq▶

点击此处观看世界纪录：https://youtu.be/jkwzJMapPeU

我的频道通常关注赛跑中较为随意的一面。通过这些视频，我想展示很酷的速跑，解释它们是如何工作的，并进行娱乐。希望你喜欢这些内容，甚至可以自己参加速跑，因为它真的很有趣！

#EazySpeezy #DuckLife #SpeedRun
